<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.3.4">
<l>vacaiyaṟu kuṟaḷāy māvali vēḷvi maṇṇaḷa viṭṭavaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yacaivaṟu mamara raṭiyiṇai vaṇaṅka valaikaṭal tuyiṉṟavam māṉai</l>
<l>ticaimuka ṉaṉaiyōr nāṅkainaṉ ṉaṭuvuḷ cempoṉcey kōyili ṉuḷḷē</l>
<l>yuyarmaṇi makuṭañ cūṭiniṉ ṟāṉaik kaṇṭukoṇ ṭuyntoḻin tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen for myself, within the Cempoṉcey Temple</l>
<l rend="indent">right in the center of Nāṅkai with people like [Brahmā]</l>
<l rend="indent">facing the directions,</l>
<l>The one who, as a faultless dwarf, took the measure of the earth</l>
<l rend="indent">at Māvali’s sacrifice,</l>
<l>The lord who sleeps on the crashing sea, as unflagging immortals</l>
<l rend="indent">worship both of [his] feet,</l>
<l>The one who stands crowned with a high, jeweled diadem,</l>
<l rend="indent">being saved, I was at ease.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
